          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced <span class=\"text-highlight\">shallot</span></strong><span class=\"text-highlight\">&nbsp;</span>and cook for 5 min or until softened</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1131.step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, line a baking tray with <strong>tin foil</strong> and add the <strong>salmon</strong> and <strong>marinade</strong> (scrunch up the edges of tin foil to stop the marinade escaping!)</p>\r\n<p>Put the tray in the oven for 5-7 min or until the<strong> salmon</strong> is cooked through</p>\r\n<p>Tip: your fish is cooked when it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
